{"tid":1627680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「無良小販」又黎食人血饅頭！","createTime":"2019-10-05T17:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:17:18.000Z","uid":54256,"like":302,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"e5c22c07236f5796804ffea813169fe3eeefda42","tid":1627680,"uid":54256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:10:17.000Z","msg":"是咁的 29/9 果日我做左一日小販<br />\n主力賣60926 同60928K<br />\n聽日銅鑼灣有人擺檔賣裝食人血饅頭！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1600750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1600750</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n29/9 果日好多恩客表示：<br />\n喂 屌你 有冇豬咀呀？ 淨係得filter 我用條撚呀？ <br />\n然後有好多人用錢掟鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然今次返嘅貨真係唔多 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">得十幾套雙罐豬咀</span></span><br />\n但返左好多和理非同中後排用嘅3200 + 3311K<br />\n等和理非都可以開心購物<br />\n或者你會問：做咩今次唔賣60926？ <br />\n我會答你：我仲未返到貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雙罐就唔會主動售賣嫁啦<br />\n你真係有需要用雙罐嘅就埋黎講通關密語：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母邊有錢買呀！</span></span><br />\n你就會獲得限量販售嘅6200+60926 / 7500+501+N95濾綿 一套<br />\n<br />\n時間：大隊出發後<br />\n地點：軒尼詩道<br />\n我地呢班喪盡天良嘅小販決定今次係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">免費取用，自由奉獻</span></span><br />\n<br />\n黎啦！蝕到我甩褲啦！<br />\n賣哂就走嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望遲啲會見到更加多無良惡德商人，一齊打劫和理非，接濟前線手足！<br />\n<br />\n今次懶得影貨物圖，用上次啲圖呃鳩大家算<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NLM4q9c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNLM4q9c.png&h=76348710&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"763b16d41d92d524833be792577ca9f46ec78bd6","tid":1627680,"uid":54256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:11:09.000Z","msg":"聽日見啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c647ed99ef7f5eaddef54407d0cb4f31bf3f885e","tid":1627680,"uid":312526,"like":1,"disl